# Build context is the repo root. Keep it lean and host-agnostic:
# node_modules are reinstalled inside the image from package-lock.json.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.vite
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Secrets & local env (never bake into images)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# VCS / editor / OS
.git
.github
.gitignore
.vscode
.idea
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Logs, coverage, uploads
**/*.log
**/coverage
backend/uploads

# Docs & scratch not needed at build time
docs
*.md
!frontend/README.md
